7. What makes it work

Hyperstition works through 6 mechanisms.

A. Attention shaping

Stories change what you notice.

B. Salience amplification

Some paths feel more charged, so you act on them sooner.

C. Identity binding

Narratives can stabilize behavior by linking action to self-concept.

D. Coordination

Shared stories let multiple minds align faster.

E. Memory compression

A symbol carries a whole protocol.

F. Persistence under uncertainty

A compelling frame helps you keep moving before full proof exists.

None of that requires mysticism.
It just means:

narrative is an execution technology

